## Workflow Orchestration

| User Intent | Skill / Workflow |
|---|---|
| Start a new feature | `/feature-start` → `.claude/workflows/feature-workflow.md` |
| Review what worked after a feature | `/retro` → `.claude/skills/retro.md` |
| Pull upstream template improvements | `/sync-bootstrap` → `.claude/skills/sync-bootstrap.md` |

## Consultation Points

Claude **must stop and get user approval** before:
1. Transitioning from Stage 1 (planning) to Stage 2 (implementation)
2. Transitioning from Stage 2 (implementation) to Stage 3 (commit)
3. Propagating findings from retro to the bootstrap template
4. Any destructive git operation

